#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.21"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.21:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 3. Vajjisattakavagga → vajjīvaggo (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an7.21:0.2"
msgid "3. Vajjisattakavagga"
msgstr "3. The Vajji Seven"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.21:0.3"
msgid "21. Sārandadasutta"
msgstr "21. At Sārandada"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "an7.21:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "an7.21:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati sārandade cetiye."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Vesālī, at the Sarandada Tree-shrine."

msgctxt "an7.21:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho sambahulā licchavī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho te "
"licchavī bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then several Licchavis went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and the Buddha said to these Licchavis:"

#. VAR: aparihāniye → aparihānīye (mr)
msgctxt "an7.21:1.4"
msgid "“satta vo, licchavī, aparihāniye dhamme desessāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Licchavis, I will teach you these seven principles that prevent decline."

msgctxt "an7.21:1.5"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "an7.21:1.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te licchavī bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "an7.21:1.7"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:2.1"
msgid "“Katame ca, licchavī, satta aparihāniyā dhammā?"
msgstr "“And what are the seven principles that prevent decline?"

msgctxt "an7.21:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjī abhiṇhaṃ sannipātā bhavissanti sannipātabahulā;"
msgstr "As long as the Vajjis meet frequently and have many meetings,"

msgctxt "an7.21:2.3"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (1)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:3.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjī samaggā sannipatissanti, samaggā "
"vuṭṭhahissanti, samaggā vajjikaraṇīyāni karissanti;"
msgstr ""
"As long as the Vajjis meet in harmony, leave in harmony, and carry on their "
"business in harmony,"

msgctxt "an7.21:3.2"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (2)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:4.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjī apaññattaṃ na paññāpessanti, paññattaṃ na "
"samucchindissanti, yathāpaññatte porāṇe vajjidhamme samādāya vattissanti;"
msgstr ""
"As long as the Vajjis don’t make new decrees or abolish existing decrees, "
"but undertake and follow the traditional Vajjian principles as they have "
"been decreed,"

msgctxt "an7.21:4.2"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (3)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjī ye te vajjīnaṃ vajjimahallakā te sakkarissanti "
"garuṃ karissanti mānessanti pūjessanti, tesañca sotabbaṃ maññissanti;"
msgstr ""
"As long as the Vajjis honor, respect, esteem, and venerate Vajjian elders, "
"and think them worth listening to,"

msgctxt "an7.21:5.2"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (4)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

# The word “rape” traditionally means to forcible abduct a woman, and has only latterly come to have exclusively sense of sexual violence. In this context it is clear that sexual violence is intended so we should use the actual word. As far as I know, this is the earliest statement anywhere in the world that not only condemns rape, but makes the connection between abolishing violence against women and the prosperity of a society.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:6.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjī yā tā kulitthiyo kulakumāriyo tā na okassa "
"pasayha vāsessanti;"
msgstr ""
"As long as the Vajjians don’t rape or abduct women or girls from their "
"families and force them to live with them,"

msgctxt "an7.21:6.2"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (5)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:7.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjī yāni tāni vajjīnaṃ vajjicetiyāni abbhantarāni "
"ceva bāhirāni ca tāni sakkarissanti garuṃ karissanti mānessanti pūjessanti, "
"tesañca dinnapubbaṃ katapubbaṃ dhammikaṃ baliṃ no parihāpessanti;"
msgstr ""
"As long as the Vajjis honor, respect, esteem, and venerate the Vajjian "
"shrines, whether inner or outer, not neglecting the proper spirit-offerings "
"that were given and made in the past,"

msgctxt "an7.21:7.2"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (6)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an7.21:8.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ arahantesu dhammikā rakkhāvaraṇagutti "
"susaṃvihitā bhavissati:"
msgstr ""
"As long as the Vajjis arrange for proper protection, shelter, and security "
"for perfected ones, so that"

msgctxt "an7.21:8.2"
msgid ""
"‘kinti anāgatā ca arahanto vijitaṃ āgaccheyyuṃ, āgatā ca arahanto vijite "
"phāsuṃ vihareyyun’ti;"
msgstr ""
"more perfected ones might come to the realm and those already here may live "
"in comfort,"

msgctxt "an7.21:8.3"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihāni. (7)"
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
#. VAR: vajjīsu ṭhassanti → vattissanti (mr)
#. VAR: sandississanti → sandissanti (bj, mr)
msgctxt "an7.21:9.1"
msgid ""
"Yāvakīvañca, licchavī, ime satta aparihāniyā dhammā vajjīsu ṭhassanti, imesu "
"ca sattasu aparihāniyesu dhammesu vajjī sandississanti;"
msgstr ""
"As long as these seven principles that prevent decline last among the "
"Vajjians, and as long as the Vajjians are seen following them,"

msgctxt "an7.21:9.2"
msgid "vuddhiyeva, licchavī, vajjīnaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā, no parihānī”ti."
msgstr "they can expect growth, not decline.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.21:9.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
